### 1. Create an article
POST http://localhost:5000/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{ "title": "Hello World", "content": "My first article", "author": "Alice" }

### 2. Get ALL articles
GET http://localhost:5000/articles

### 3. Get ONE article
GET http://localhost:5000/articles/1

### 4. Update an article
PUT http://localhost:5000/articles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{ "title": "Updated Title", "content": "Updated content", "author": "Alice" }

### 5. Delete an article
DELETE http://localhost:5000/articles/1
```

---

## Step 4 — This is what you'll see

After pasting, a small grey **"Send Request"** link will appear **above every `###` block**, like this:
```
Send Request          ← 👈 click this!
### 1. Create an article
POST http://localhost:5000/articles
...
